languages.text: "Какое общество, какие лица!.. Право, отправиться на Даргонус стоило бы и без знакомства с вами, шерин. Этот мир дает огромный простор для ведения дел!"
"Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"

languages.text: “如此辉煌的社会！如此富裕的贵族！说真的，亲爱的，就算我不认识你，也应该来达戈努斯一趟。这个世界有着无数做生意的机会！”

traits.locale_text: “如此辉煌的社会！如此富裕的贵族！说真的，亲爱的，就算我不认识你，也应该来达戈努斯一趟。这个世界有着无数做生意的机会！”

languages.text: «¡Qué sociedad tan ilustre! ¡Y qué nobles más educados! Valdría la pena venir a Dargonus incluso sin conocerte, shereen. ¡Este mundo ofrece un sinfín de posibilidades empresariales!».
languages.original_text: "Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"

traits.locale_text: «¡Qué sociedad tan ilustre! ¡Y qué nobles más educados! Valdría la pena venir a Dargonus incluso sin conocerte, shereen. ¡Este mundo ofrece un sinfín de posibilidades empresariales!».

languages.text: 「輝かしい社会！金持ちの貴族ども！確かにアンタを知るつもりなんかなくてもダルゴナスを訪れる価値はあるね、シャリーン。この星はビジネスを展開する大きな可能性を秘めている！」
languages.original_text: "Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"

traits.locale_text: 「輝かしい社会！金持ちの貴族ども！確かにアンタを知るつもりなんかなくてもダルゴナスを訪れる価値はあるね、シャリーン。この星はビジネスを展開する大きな可能性を秘めている！」

languages.text: "Was für eine illustre Gesellschaft! Derart betuchte Adlige! Wahrlich, Dargonus wäre einen Besuch wert, auch wenn ich Euch nicht kennen würde, Shereen. Diese Welt eröffnet enorme Möglichkeiten für Geschäfte!"
languages.original_text: "Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"

languages.text: « Quelle société illustre ! Quelle opulence parmi la noblesse ! Même sans en profiter pour faire plus ample connaissance, shereen, Dargonus mérite bien qu'on s'y arrête. Ce monde regorge d'opportunités commerciales ! »
languages.original_text: "Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"

languages.text: "Nasıl da şanlı bir sosyeteymiş bu! Soyluların ensesi de pek kalınmış! Seninle tanımasaydım bile Dargonus'u ziyaret etmeye değermiş şirinim. Bu dünyada iş fırsatından bol şey yok!"
languages.original_text: "Such illustrious society! Such well-heeled nobles! Indeed, it would be worth visiting Dargonus even without getting to know you, shereen. This world offers huge scope for doing business!"
